name: 8. The Melted Truck.
description:
"The Toyota Hilux, most indestructible pickup, ute type 4wd vehicle in the world. Will still run after bring submerged in the ocean according to Top Gear.. I think this maybe took it beyond that capacity. The windscreen had melted, curving over the dashboard like some kind of surrealist clock. The beautiful timber floored tray had completely disappeared. The random box of glass bottles left on the seat now a similarly melted blob. I honestly didn't think that was possible. But I hadn't seen my caravan yet.."

Photography by Jay Moon, during the Australian wildfires; November 2019.
#8 of 15.
All funds generated go toward the ongoing recovery.
